org.nd4j.autodiff.listeners.impl

Class UIListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nd4j.autodiff.listeners.BaseListener
      • org.nd4j.autodiff.listeners.impl.UIListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Listener

    public class UIListener
extends BaseListener
    User interface listener for SameDiff

    Basic usage: 
     
 UIListener l = UIListener.builder(f)
                  //Plot loss curve, at every iteration (enabled and set to 1 by default)
                 .plotLosses(1)
                 //Plot the training set evaluation metrics: accuracy and f1 score
                 .trainEvaluationMetrics("softmax", 0, Evaluation.Metric.ACCURACY, Evaluation.Metric.F1)
                 //Plot the parameter to update:ratios for each parameter, every 10 iterations
                 .updateRatios(10)
                 .build();

    Note that the UIListener supports continuing with the same network on the same file - but only if the network configuration matches. See UIListener.FileMode for configuration/details
    Author:
    Alex Black
